      "reason": "No distributed tracing, no correlation IDs, no metrics, no alerting. The team cannot detect, diagnose, or quantify any of the failure modes identified above. The timeout mismatch alone will produce symptoms (intermittent checkout failures, orphaned orders) that are nearly impossible to debug without request-level tracing across all three services.",
      "routed_to": "Coach K"
    }
  ],

